title.rendered: Taj777 News has partnered with the Balla Bol T10 cricket league as a ‘Powered By’ sponsor

content.rendered:
A new cricket league introducing “Balla Bol” is a T10 Cricket League powered by Taj777 News. Balla Bol is a T10 Cricket League in which teams play a single innings, which is restricted to a maximum of ten overs (60 legal balls) per side, with the game lasting approximately 90 minutes. The first competition using this format took place in Dec 2017, the opening season of the T10 Cricket League in the UAE. The International Cricket Council (ICC) officially sanctioned the league.

Get Best Odds & Fancy on Live Sports on Taj777

 The League will played from 3 July to 10 July. The all matches of the league played in Gaziabad. Here is the full schedule of Balla Bol League:
